{"sections":{"523995f1-77dc-4293-9056-7c2bbd99683d":{"type":"text-with-media","blocks":{"template--16183500669097__523995f1-77dc-4293-9056-7c2bbd99683d-image-1":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/230904_NMJ_15__2376.jpg","mobile_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/230904_NMJ_15__2376.jpg"}}},"block_order":["template--16183500669097__523995f1-77dc-4293-9056-7c2bbd99683d-image-1"],"settings":{"remove_spacing_top":false,"remove_spacing_bottom":true,"enable_newsletter_subscribe":false,"klaviyo_form_id":"","media_position":"right","media_width":"7","content_position":"middleLeft","subheading":"<p><strong>COMMUNITY<\/strong><\/p>","title":"<p>Introducing Terra |<em> Styled in collaboration with Lee Mathews<\/em><\/p>","description":"<p>Design inspiration is found in myriad places, and our role as creators is to translate the conceptual into pieces you’ll treasure forever. For our five-piece Terra capsule collection, we looked to Mother Nature as muse.<\/p><p>Echoing the natural world’s evolving temperament, the collection’s name – Terra – derives from the Latin phrase “Goddess of the earth; the earth itself”.<\/p><p>We love collaborating with likeminded Australian brands and iconic fashion designer <a href=\"https:\/\/leemathews.com.au\/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/leemathews.com.au\/\"><em><strong>Lee Mathews<\/strong><\/em><\/a> shares our creative sensibility; seeking inspiration in the realms of art, design and craftsmanship. Her pieces evoke a similar creative perspective to our own collections – unifying classic silhouettes with unexpected details, with an emphasis on luxurious wardrobe staples. <\/p><p><\/p><p>Join us as we pair the Terra Collection with pieces from Lee’s latest collection.<\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_style":"underline"}},"3ebc68a8-39a5-4ef0-96ec-3daf87a7a4fc":{"type":"seo-copy","settings":{"title":"","content_intro":"<p><strong>Terra Necklace | Diamond<\/strong><\/p><p>An extension of our organic design sensibility, this special <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nataliemariejewellery.com\/products\/terra-necklace-diamond-yellow-gold?_pos=3&_sid=55ee2f68e&_ss=r\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.nataliemariejewellery.com\/products\/terra-necklace-diamond-yellow-gold?_pos=3&_sid=55ee2f68e&_ss=r\">Terra Diamond Necklace<\/a> pays homage to the perfect imperfection of the elements; to the natural world’s perpetually shifting, changing and evolving beauty. Handmade to order in 9ct yellow, rose and white gold, this silhouette is intended as an elevated everyday classic – a unique yet timeless addition to your personal curation. <\/p>","content":""}},"9413ffab-ce0b-4d8a-9c65-c186f70057a9":{"type":"content-list","blocks":{"template--16183500669097__9413ffab-ce0b-4d8a-9c65-c186f70057a9-image-2":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/230904_NMJ_13__2051_ba88a898-0d9f-42d8-820b-6a6cfc291c25.jpg","apply_overlay":false,"devices":"mobile_desktop","content_position":"underLeft","subheading":"","title":"","description":"","description_mobile":"","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_2_text":"","button_2_link":"","button_style":"underline","include_no_media_border":true,"metaobject_autoplay":"","metaobject_loop":"","metaobject_apply_overlay":"","metaobject_content_position":"","metaobject_colour_style":"","metaobject_button_style":"","metaobject_devices":""}},"template--16183500669097__9413ffab-ce0b-4d8a-9c65-c186f70057a9-image-1":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/230904_NMJ_13__2062_9f48f5b5-d298-4fab-b3de-7adcda16a0fd.jpg","apply_overlay":false,"devices":"mobile_desktop","content_position":"underLeft","subheading":"","title":"","description":"","description_mobile":"","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_2_text":"","button_2_link":"","button_style":"underline","include_no_media_border":true,"metaobject_autoplay":"","metaobject_loop":"","